    "description": "Join the Curefit Consulting Pvt Ltd family as a Senior Software Engineer in Gwalior. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Curefit Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nCurefit Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Curefit Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
